<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Yeah I agree, towards the end of the book it mentions that her Ma, herself and Jason are living in a nice home, whilst she works as a surgeon. However<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Yeah I agree, towards the end of the book it mentions that her Ma, herself and Jason are living in a nice home, whilst she works as a surgeon. However I do hope she has no good fortunes due to the way she treated Kimberley and her Ma. Even though Aunt Paula helped the both of them get out of Hong Kong she was not happy for their successes and if they became more successful than her she would become jealous of them and try to degrade Kimberley. But towards the end Kimberley and her Ma tell Aunt Paula about their new apartment and Kimberley's scholarship to Yale, there they tell Aunt Paula to leave them alone and not to bother them or they would expose her for the factory's piece payment and working conditions. :))<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
